Package com.milk.command

Interface Summary
Command A Command is a user-activatable action of some sort.
Commandable A Commandable is an object that has an associated list of user commands.
CommandableListener This is the interface for objects that care about CommandableEvents.
CommandListener This is the interface for objects that care about CommandEvents.
 

Class Summary
BaseCommand This is a base class which implements most of the standard Command functionality.
CommandableEvent This is the class for events having to do with happenings on a Commandable.
CommandEvent This is the class for events having to do with happenings on a Command.
CommandList This is a handy class for holding a list of zero or more Commands.
 

Exception Summary
DisabledCommandException This exception is thrown when Command.run() is called, but the command in question is disabled.
